&lt;h2 id=&quot;personal-goals&quot;&gt;Personal Goals&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn more about Computer Graphics in general.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get familiar with designing complex software.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use multi-threading effectively&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
